data.description: AGENTS & BUYERS, DON'T MISS THIS ONE! Updated and MOVE IN READY with immediate occupancy! This wonderful home is at the end of a private cul-de-sac in the heavily sought Fox Run neighborhood of Columbia. Oversize great room, some fresh paint, updated carpet, water filtration system, elevated storage in garage, a formal dining room (a rarity to find) and more. Updated, clean and move in ready. Updated kitchen with oak cabinetry and new drop lighting and eat at bar. The backyard is complete with a storage building and a custom multi level deck perfect for entertaining and relaxing. The rear yard is extremely private and backs up to a large wildlife filled woods. Large bedrooms with spacious closets. Asphalt driveway with level parking area outside garage. Great location with easy access to US 43 and I-65. All kitchen appliances remain. Convenient to shopping, restaurants, grocery, schools, and more! This place deserves to be looked at, there is nothing else like it available.
